        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Devices Spectramax</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Plus</ENAMEX>) and a <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Qiagen Bio-Robot 3000</ENAMEX> was
        used to dilute the <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">DNA samples</ENAMEX> to <ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">500 ng/Î¼l</ENAMEX> in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">2X</TIMEX> spotting
        solution. Tests showed that the combination of Superamine
