        patterns of regulation of specific transcripts were
        observed and several examples of the differentially
        regulated genes are indicated in Figure <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4</NUMEX>. Qualitatively
        similar results using a direct <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">RNA</ENAMEX>-dye coupling procedure
        can be achieved using the <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Micromaxâ¢ ASAP RNA Labeling Kit</ENAMEX>
        (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Perkin Elmer Life Sciences</ENAMEX>, Inc. <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">cat</ENAMEX>. No. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">MPS544</NUMEX>)
        following the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">manufacturer</ENAMEX>'s suggested protocol. While it
